summary: I made my own ENB in trying to make Skyrim as real as possible. Well in my opinion...your welcome to argue.
descriptionHtml:
Thank you Very Much for Downloading
Put all of the files in the skyrim directory thank you 
DoF use dynavison by gopher (enb DoF was giving me issues if it works for you use it its better then dynavision)
AO use nvidia control panel (also giving me issues) 
This ENB was based on Jamin\'s ENB 4_4 i just changed a few codes and commands around. 
(Please forgive my foul tone) 

(Original ENB link)
 http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/12549/

let me give you my pc tech specs and how the enb runs. And then see how your pc compares. 

I have a 
(2) GTX 560 TI both 1gb cards 
Intel 3770 CPU at 3.6 ghz (4 physical and 4 virtual cores) in total 8 cores. 
Sabertooth Z77 Motherboard 
16gb of g.skills DDR3 ram running at 1800mhz
(2) WD black 2TB hard drives in raid 0 7200rpm 
850 watts psu 
h100 cpu coller 

All of this i barley get 34fps in busy cities such as whiterun and markarth and around 58 fps in the middle of no where in the ice fields. 
Here is a video showing the ENB in action 
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n_hkD_hd7rM
